balanceOfBatch(address[],uint256[]).details: See {IKIP37-balanceOfBatch}. Requirements: - `owners` and `ids` must have the same length.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner.
